        "69081": {
          "vnum": 69081,
          "name": "Within Ingeen",
          "description": "A few small houses have been squeezed between the oaks in a small clearing here. A short wooden sign quietly declares that you have come upon the village of Ingeen. Hobbits wander about tending to their day- to-day chores, and darker hobbits clad in robes can be seen performing complex chants. Passage to the north is blocked by a fallen oak, but can be surpassed by shifting a large branch. Huts lie to the east and west, and the village opens out to the south.",
