          "vnum": 69082,
          "name": "Ingeen Guard House",
          "description": "As you enter the small hut and take in your surroundings, you realize it reminds you of a guard house back home. A bay window in the eastern wall allows a glimpse of the deep oak forest beyond the hut, and allows the guards to feel closer to their native element. The hut expands to the south, and to the west lies an opening leading back out into the village.",
