        "69084": {
          "vnum": 69084,
          "name": "The Golden Flame",
          "description": "Ducking your head, you step beneath a large sign and cross the threshold. A faint continuous noise emanates from within, and upon further inspection, you discover that the source of the light rustle is the vast collection of magical tomes that fill the bookshelves along the walls. The highly enchanted pages flutter as if a brisk wind filled the room. A doorway to the northwest leads back out into the village.",
