        "69086": {
          "vnum": 69086,
          "name": "The House of Djeen",
          "description": "A fierce wind howls inexplicably through the house, leaving nothing untouched. The carpet has been torn asunder, and articles of furniture have long since been swept away. A massive cage has been bolted into the floor to your west, and a threatening growl can be heard from within. Dull light pulses from the bottom of a twisting flight of steps, perhaps from some sort of basement, and a door to the north leads out of the house.",
