        "69089": {
          "vnum": 69089,
          "name": "Deep Within the Ingeen Tree",
          "description": "Your senses reel as your soul is immersed in the utter evil of this dank chamber. From here, the spirit of the tree manipulates the unsuspecting hobbits of Ingeen, using them for its own gains. The chamber is unbearably hot, and you feel a pulsing pain course rhythmically through your body like a diabolical heart beat. A wooden ladder fastened to the wall leads upward out of the darkness.",
