        "69090": {
          "vnum": 69090,
          "name": "The Secret Laboratory",
          "description": "Deviously hidden, the secret laboratory allows Djeen to work without interruption. Viles of oddly smoking solutions and cages containing chittering creatures fill the room, but are dwarfed by the size of Djeen`s book collection. Magical tomes and volumes fill the bookshelves, some Djeen`s own, some borrowed from other mages of power. A spiral flight of stairs leads back up into the cage of Djeen`s familiar above.",
