        "69092": {
          "vnum": 69092,
          "name": "Ayine`s Room",
          "description": "Stepping through the doorway and escaping the howling gale, you enter this comparably normal room. As you fix your hair and adjust your clothing, you realize that there is however something odd about this room. It won`t sit still. Perhaps because a pair of daemonlings scurry about constantly rearranging things. A doorway to the north leads away from the crazy little things.",
