        "69096": {
          "vnum": 69096,
          "name": "Ingeen School of Magic",
          "description": "The interior of this small school calls to mind your early school days, only it is somehow strangely different. The desks float gently a few inches above the ground, the chalkboard glows with a soft blue light, and a faint hum can be heard in the air. A thin flight of stairs at the back of the room lead upward, the fresh air of the village center lies to the north, and a door engraved with three adjacent stars allows passage to the south.",
          "grid_x": 0,
