        "69099": {
          "vnum": 69099,
          "name": "Weapon Smithy",
          "description": "A bright red glow burns in the fiery hearth of this hut. Great clouds of mist billow upward, accompanied by resounding fizzles as the weapon smith dips molten hot metal into cool tubs of water. Weapons of splendor adorn the walls, sure to be magically bound to ward off unwanted thieves. The doorway to the east leads out of the oppressive heat and humidity.",
